
The GlideDateTime class provides methods for performing operations on GlideDateTime objects, such as:
  - instantiating GlideDateTime objects.
  - working with glide_date_time fields.

The GlideDateTime methods are used to perform date-time operations, such as:
  - instantiating a GlideDateTime object, 
  - performing date-time calculations, 
  - formatting a date-time, 
  - converting between date-time formats.
  
  The GlideDateTime API is used to manipulate date and time values.
